{"tid":1701073,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"唔好忘記7/11登打士街死者","createTime":"2019-11-08T23:15:08.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-10T12:13:41.000Z","uid":99701,"like":98,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":58,"replies":[{"pid":"fa4d883c27de2ad0877b03c7d9a1f327666abafc","tid":1701073,"uid":99701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-08T23:15:08.000Z","msg":"星期四6點鐘左右，男死者當時伏屍登打士街休憩處(即係家樂坊旁邊)近門口一處草叢，全身赤裸，死不瞑目，除口鼻有血外全身都無血<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n呢單係呢場運動最離譜最心寒嘅屍體發現！<br />\n1.首先係喺旺角6點鐘人流咁旺地方，事發一刻有巨響引嚟好多人旁觀，我相信有好多人目擊經過<br />\n2.光天化日明目張膽<br />\n3.又係全裸「自殺」(狗當然又話無可疑)<br />\n4.有唔只一個目擊者話死者墮下時身體捲曲，似被人dum落街，死狀亦唔似自殺<br />\n5.無乜主流媒體報(得蘋果、01、大紀元)，離奇得嚟曝光率奇低<br />\n<br />\n香港人唔可以慣咗日日都有人離奇死亡<br />\n死者曾經係一個有名有姓有血有肉嘅人！<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">唔可以畀佢死得不明不白</span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"a2ffb10414cd596899243241996f0b74b143c780","tid":1701073,"uid":69334,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-08T23:16:31.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"6b3be711643f158dfc1cd6fc8805d9d09f6ffe35","tid":1701073,"uid":165361,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-08T23:21:26.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"b91d7e507a0d8a7c64c614a69cabe0ee9a1767b6","tid":1701073,"uid":99701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-08T23:25:46.000Z","msg":"推到有目擊者入嚟"},{"pid":"4967488de23841682096f6ac9315082955fee749","tid":1701073,"uid":60916,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-08T23:26:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"22f85ceee1090e46dfc7af0f374b915c6ef313b3","tid":1701073,"uid":49300,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-08T23:37:05.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"eb2c24851ba063acfd26d7e8f451d34ba0e6fab3","tid":1701073,"uid":89006,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-08T23:37:54.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"4122633f8cf2a9c3