ces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fabd7381728859b7d60470561b8847e687c1cb5e","tid":1701073,"uid":321837,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fa4d883c27de2ad0877b03c7d9a1f327666abafc","tid":1701073,"uid":99701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-08T23:15:08.000Z","msg":"星期四6點鐘左右，男死者當時伏屍登打士街休憩處(即係家樂坊旁邊)近門口一處草叢，全身赤裸，死不瞑目，除口鼻有血外全身都無血<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n呢單係呢場運動最離譜最心寒嘅屍體發現！<br />\n1.首先係喺旺角6點鐘人流咁旺地方，事發一刻有巨響引嚟好多人旁觀，我相信有好多人目擊經過<br />\n2.光天化日明目張膽<br />\n3.又係全裸「自殺」(狗當然又話無可疑)<br />\n4.有唔只一個目擊者話死者墮下時身體捲曲，似被人dum落街，死狀亦唔似自殺<br />\n5.無乜主流媒體報(得蘋果、01、大紀元)，離奇得嚟曝光率奇低<br />\n<br />\n香港人唔可以慣咗日日都有人離奇死亡<br />\n死者曾經係一個有名有姓有血有肉嘅人！<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">唔可以畀佢死得不明不白</span></span></strong>"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-09T02:24:39.000Z","msg":"普通身形定係大隻架?"},{"pid":"a6a0f9fe9b2d3bee106517d082a109109a502c37","tid":1701073,"uid":48057,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-09T02:26:08.000Z","msg":"pish"},{"pid":"4ea5708604fb2c64dae84b44d7f0a398fbc3d51f","tid":1701073,"uid":224869,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-09T02:27:23.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"9d6c62e295aa20f0a869cf25d21f9c040732a13e","tid":1701073,"uid":11809,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-09T02:38:28.000Z","msg":"香港人唔會忘記"},{"pid":"653d4300b007cf7b1becbfce0d810ba41e40574f","tid":1701073,"uid":141645,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-09T02:39:12.000Z","msg":"推！"},{"pid":"36ce9a20b9807211ee129358aec75e2e031a9007","tid":1701073,"uid":158235,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-09T02:40:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"62c0a7c68a696c2b8928cc174f